ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e77caa23908a59d683cc441bc53518264ef266","tid":901275,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"933fa6d9daa801090e67c035b3727af28e7d9f86","tid":901275,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8df56b5299086e7f6a4c6230a7e1279b4c8127fd","tid":901275,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a66efe0ad5263a9f8a1380b853ddd8b581b7add9","tid":901275,"uid":7350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:46:05.000Z","msg":"早幾年去見識過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇見個門口都唔想入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRS01KV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRS01KV.png&h=78688b72&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T04:39:35.000Z","msg":"唔係話好核突 但都無話有咩特別 如果唔係有咩安全問題 其實無必要拆姐, 都係歷史一部份"},{"pid":"0939d287414d3916458a8db23db45f2c27ce34d5","tid":901275,"uid":38172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"在吉田寮里不只有學生，還有寵物，家畜。因為在這裏可以養各種小動物，別說雞鴨，就是你想養頭牛都是可以有的。在這裏幾乎沒有犯法一說，焰火報警隨時因為有人做飯而響起，在牆上也會貼着打倒校長的標語。在這裏進屋不需要拖鞋，睡覺時男女同寢，並且一旦你起夜上廁所。在想回到自己的被窩很難找到。不僅男女同寢，洗手間也是男女通用。經常會出現男生一早在小便池上廁所，女生在對面洗漱，而且還會問聲「おはよう」早上好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}